# No Assuming

- Follow user instructions literally.
- Do not add, change, rename, or remove anything not explicitly requested.
- If any instruction is ambiguous, ask one concise clarification question before editing.
- Make the smallest possible change set that satisfies the exact request.
- Do not include extra "helpful" refactors, copy edits, UI tweaks, or side fixes unless explicitly asked.

